<i>My dear Frodo:</i>

2
00:01:13,071 --> 00:01:14,738
<i>You asked me once...</i>

3
00:01:14,739 --> 00:01:19,618
<i>...if I had told you everything
there was to know about my adventures.</i>

4
00:01:19,619 --> 00:01:20,911
<i>And while I can honestly...</i>

5
00:01:20,912 --> 00:01:22,204
<i>...say I have told you...</i>

6
00:01:22,205 --> 00:01:24,581
<i>...the truth...</i>

7
00:01:24,582 --> 00:01:29,582
<i>...I may not have told you all of it.</i>

8
00:01:34,884 --> 00:01:38,428
<i>I am old now, Frodo.</i>

9
00:01:38,429 --> 00:01:43,429
<i>I'm not the same Hobbit I once was.</i>

10
00:01:44,477 --> 00:01:46,186
<i>I think...</i>

11
00:01:46,187 --> 00:01:49,189
<i>...it is time for you to know...</i>

12
00:01:49,190 --> 00:01:53,360
<i>...what really happened.</i>

13
